org.codemonkey.swiftsocketclient
Class ClientEndpointTCP

java.lang.Object
  org.codemonkey.swiftsocketclient.ClientEndpointTCP
All Implemented Interfaces:
ClientEndpoint
 class ClientEndpointTCP
extends Object
implements ClientEndpoint

Wrapper that delegates all calls directly to the decorated Socket. The Client Endpoint abstraction mimics how TCP deals with a server and so the TCP client endpoint variant adds no extra functionality, except that it returns the server endpoint instead of the Socket instance itself (see getServerEndpoint().

Since:
1.0
Author:
Benny Bottema
